  "title": "【重新发布】SuperMemo 18 中文懒人包",
  "image_width": 1157,
  "content": "<h2>版权声明⚠️</h2><p data-pid=\"VP5LdcxY\">目前已经从懒人包中清除了方正字体和 SuperMemo 密钥，希望大家支持正版。</p><h2>简介</h2><p data-pid=\"tWzio98_\">本项目旨在提供开箱即用的 SuperMemo 18 程序，方便学习者快速上手 SuperMemo 和渐进阅读。</p><h2>鸣谢</h2><p data-pid=\"cuptTNga\">感谢 <a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/0a95419f5dafdedf6ba306df39df7210\" class=\"internal\">@外接式赛博格</a>帮忙调整默认设置，以及添加预设语言学习模板。</p><h2>下载</h2><h3>GitHub</h3><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//github.com/L-M-Sherlock/sm18-lazy-package/releases/\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://</span><span class=\"visible\">github.com/L-M-Sherlock</span><span class=\"invisible\">/sm18-lazy-package/releases/</span><span class=\"ellipsis\"></span></a><h3>百度网盘</h3><p data-pid=\"rB9tUIwm\">链接：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//pan.baidu.com/s/1deK5w_zfwUhS7oLJ0jF0qQ\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://</span><span class=\"visible\">pan.baidu.com/s/1deK5w_</span><span class=\"invisible\">zfwUhS7oLJ0jF0qQ</span><span class=\"ellipsis\"></span></a> </p><p data-pid=\"xzPTVOkH\">提取码：cw8t </p><h2>使用方法</h2><p data-pid=\"8GF7Z3zX\">解压后得到三个文件夹</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-8fc6e43b067512a847288a7a500a56c7_b.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"272\" data-rawheight=\"122\" class=\"content_image\" width=\"272\" data-original-token=\"v2-8fc6e43b067512a847288a7a500a56c7\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"P3ts3f-H\">先打开字体文件夹安装里面的两个字体。</p><p data-pid=\"xDFOcvxX\">然后打开 sm18 文件夹，运行 sm18.exe 开箱即用。</p><p data-pid=\"D2zOX5QO\">Quicker 文件夹中有相关的动作推荐，仅供参考。</p><h2>特色</h2><p data-pid=\"ac47gvVZ\">本懒人包实现了：</p><ul><li data-pid=\"NFe5WVqX\">界面完全汉化</li><li data-pid=\"by0kUT40\">教程完全汉化</li><li data-pid=\"vESKfb2X\">修改默认主题</li><li data-pid=\"gfxFt7Me\">修改启动画面</li><li data-pid=\"pOsk36r1\">预设护眼样式</li><li data-pid=\"uwdndF0e\">关闭巩固练习</li><li data-pid=\"_k9H71t3\">关闭算法提醒</li><li data-pid=\"T8f7B6rk\">开启自动推迟</li><li data-pid=\"oerqxwtu\">开启按钮提示</li><li data-pid=\"bjS5hYsW\">开启模板自动应用</li><li data-pid=\"EEwMsOqN\">添加语言学习模板</li><li data-pid=\"-peS4_Le\">添加TODO概念组</li><li data-pid=\"1cl9v1wr\">添加Quicker动作推荐列表</li></ul><h2>预览</h2><figure data-size=\"normal\"><img src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-e17aa2c7a6935f744967ad7bd002161a_b.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1920\" data-rawheight=\"1080\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1920\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-e17aa2c7a6935f744967ad7bd002161a_r.jpg\" data-original-token=\"v2-e17aa2c7a6935f744967ad7bd002161a\"/></figure><figure data-size=\"normal\"><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-fad8816b2d4daaadddb1dd7bea0e7dae_b.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1768\" data-rawheight=\"1254\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1768\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-fad8816b2d4daaadddb1dd7bea0e7dae_r.jpg\" data-original-token=\"v2-fad8816b2d4daaadddb1dd7bea0e7dae\"/></figure><figure data-size=\"normal\"><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-1716718068d1687e44b853b1f2d06076_b.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"332\" data-rawheight=\"454\" class=\"content_image\" width=\"332\" data-original-token=\"v2-1716718068d1687e44b853b1f2d06076\"/></figure><figure data-size=\"normal\"><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-5bdfbdd32ac32d13a51b4848f3d2bdf4_b.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"408\" data-rawheight=\"140\" class=\"content_image\" width=\"408\" data-original-token=\"v2-5bdfbdd32ac32d13a51b4848f3d2bdf4\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"XzvecG1d\">欢迎各位反馈意见或建议。</p>",
